THE KARNEY (#1-4,complete) - IDW
Writer : Bryan Johnson
Artist : Walter Flanagan

Karney tells the violent DISTURBING story of a twisted carnival that heads from town to town, entertaining the denizens of the towns while fulfilling a more sinister purpose as well. It?s chock full of sideshow characters, all rendered in twisted, loving fashion by Flanagan and digital inker/colorist Tom B. Long. But Johnson?s story delivers more than just creepy characters, too?it?s got genuine heart in places, and will have its share of pathos amongst the freaky characters.
